{"tid":2505929,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黨鐵終於回覆] 有關杏花邨青年查飛狗跪頸事件之回覆","createTime":"2021-04-27T03:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T05:00:04.000Z","uid":39218,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c419208e5e86354f2891f422257ddde67672bfa1","tid":2505929,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:50:38.000Z","msg":"4月16日 杏花邨站 事件 <br />\n港鐵公司陸續向投訴人發出回覆，<br />\n如下文- <br />\n(經比對後，為一式一樣罐頭template 回覆）<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n<br />\n本公司接獲您提交的網上意見表，就港鐵顧客服務及收益保護組職員的表現提出意見，現謹覆如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為保障已繳付正確車費乘客的利益，本公司每日均會在不同時間，以不同形式安排顧客服務及收益保護組職員根據《香港鐵路附例》執行職務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據記錄，4月16日上午約8時，顧客服務及收益保護組人員在杏花邨站進行查票工作時，留意到一名男乘客使用特惠車票岀閘，於是上前請乘客停下來進行查票工作，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">惟該乘客未有出示任何車票</span></span>，及作出激烈反應，過程中有五名職員受傷。事件現時已交由警方處理。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n我們一直就查票工作為前綫同事提供合適的培訓及支援，以適切地因應不同乘客的需要而作出相應的安排。然而，我們明白外界對事件的關注，正檢視當日查票的安排及處理。若有值得改善之處，我們必定會採取適當措施。<br />\n<br />\n此外，我們亦會與一些支援團體交流，探討日後在處理類似個案時，如何處理雙方之間的互動和溝通。<br />\n<br />\n謹此感謝您的網上意見表。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵公司<br />\n<br />\n署理公共關係經理－客務<br />\n<br />\n陳永建<br />\n<br />\nMC/kl<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">sauce：</span><a href=\"https://t.me/chafei9/482\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fchafei9%2F482&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B619PyQTEnBXXUT3Ba6PvfAw%3D&h=7e7fbf90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/chafei9/482</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"large\">其實一直都唔明，出左閘出示唔到飛點解有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇高手可以解答到我呢個疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"bb0ce9dbe198289da58885edaee1cc1326a7d0bc","tid":2505929,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:51:53.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"879acbd3281fbaa2802a2aeb6bea54b0cadb47b7","tid":2505929,"uid":32006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:52:02.000Z","msg":"封信都冇答到個問題"},{"pid":"8a451066649fbb8d556ae72f3249a1231ff64dca","tid":2505929,"uid":34383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"出左閘點俾張飛佢睇 如果係用飛"},{"pid":"9ef7ea23dfd73e830c5e6d504b3e25b56d46d9ef","tid":2505929,"uid":14983,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"有五名職員受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18374288da2e3da88f5060de8f8cd5f26c48ae67","tid":2505929,"uid":39218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"879acbd3281fbaa2802a2aeb6bea54b0cadb47b7","tid":2505929,"uid":32006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:52:02.000Z","msg":"封信都冇答到個問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:53:24.000Z","msg":"究竟出左閘點解唔可以冇飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d9c1ec45f24f89b98c46ca03cc70db8890490e","tid":2505929,"uid":39218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a451066649fbb8d556ae72f3249a1231ff64dca","tid":2505929,"uid":34383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"出左閘點俾張飛佢睇 如果係用飛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:54:43.000Z","msg":"咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba87301d937aef4b267a556220805640891b14d","tid":2505929,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326ce0562b389efd6d0404a83155fac64897da00","tid":2505929,"uid":3